er gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:52.734375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/85b06/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/bc282/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/f1720/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/85b06/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/bc282/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/f1720/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/f1720/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/85b06/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/bc282/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/f1720/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/85b06/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 256w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/bc282/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 512w,\n/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/f1720/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/488f6b6aacff73ad76185819c8f041a2/f1720/Image-12.11.20-Good-Hearts-Total-Raised-1024x538.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>In conjunction with <a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\">The PM Group’s</a> 32rd business anniversary, our agency raised a total of $215,049 in support of eight local nonprofits as a result of our annual <a href=\"https://fun-raiser.org/\">Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Fun-raiser</a>, which took place September 14-30, 2020.  In comparison to previous years, the fundraising initiative went virtual in the form of an online auction and raffle.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>All proceeds from the online auction and raffle benefited local charities serving education, at-risk children, military, family support services, as well as pet rescue efforts. This year’s benefiting organizations included:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Central Catholic High School </strong></li>\n<li><strong>God’s Dogs Rescue </strong></li>\n<li><strong>Guide Dogs of Texas</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Respite Care of San Antonio         </strong></li>\n<li><strong> </strong><strong>SA YES</strong></li>\n<li><strong>The Children’s Shelter </strong></li>\n<li><strong>Soldiers’ Angels </strong></li>\n<li><strong>San Antonio Sports</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>“Over the past 30 years, The PM Group has been fortunate enough to endure industry changes by adapting and developing innovative business models to better serve our clients and community,” said <strong>The PM Group Founder Bob Wills</strong>. “As a result, each year we show our gratitude by supporting nonprofit organizations making a difference in our city &#8211; this year was no different. We pivoted and tailored our annual Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Fun-raiser to the current climate, which yielded successful results. Thank you to our sponsors and donors who participated in our annual charitable initiative.”</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-4 is-cropped\">\n<ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\">\n<li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n<figure><span class=\"wp-image-60237 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:800px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/cee829e68483b9451306bfbbf280fdc3/f8f3a/2.png 200w,\n/static/cee829e68483b9451306bfbbf280fdc3/6a8a8/2.png 400w,\n/static/cee829e68483b9451306bfbbf280fdc3/7842b/2.png 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcSet=\"/static/cee829e68483b9451306bfbbf280fdc3/f8f3a/2.png 200w,\n/static/cee829e68483b9451306bfbbf280fdc3/6a8a8/2.png 400w,\n/static/cee829e68483b9451306bfbbf280fdc3/7842b/2.png 800w\" src=\"/static/cee829e68483b9451306bfbbf280fdc3/7842b/2.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><pictur