0vw, 800px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"/static/ccbf15f6832c84e7f7a553154d38f112/f8f3a/8.png 200w,\n/static/ccbf15f6832c84e7f7a553154d38f112/6a8a8/8.png 400w,\n/static/ccbf15f6832c84e7f7a553154d38f112/7842b/8.png 800w\" src=\"/static/ccbf15f6832c84e7f7a553154d38f112/7842b/8.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 100px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 32 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In the past 10 years, The PM Group has raised both directly and indirectly over $12 million for these charities. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Presents Over $200K to 8 Local Nonprofit Organizations","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Presents Over $200K to 8 Local Nonprofit Organizations","url":"/the-pm-group-presents-over-200k-to-8-local-nonprofit-organizations-2/"}],"title":"The PM Group Presents Over $200K to San Antonio Nonprofit Organizations","metaDesc":"The PM Group raised a total of $215,049 in support of eight local nonprofits as a result of our annual Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Fun-raiser...","focuskw":"The PM Group","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"The PM